Bringing magical moments to donut lovers worldwide, Krispy Kreme® Doughnut Corporation is a global retailer known for its premium-quality sweet treats, especially their iconic hot Original Glazed® doughnut. With headquarters in Winston-Salem, NC, the company has been delighting customers with top-notch doughnuts and delicious coffee since 1937. To find a store near you and for more information, visitwww.krispykreme.com.